chart_description: This chart displays the rate of responses per second related to HTTP cache. It may help to identify potential performance bottlenecks and optimize caching strategies.

dimension_descriptions.bypassed: The rate of responses per second bypassed by the cache due to either a miss or a stale cache entry.
dimension_descriptions.served: The rate of responses per second served by the cache.
dimension_descriptions.written: The rate of responses per second that have been written to the cache since the last restart or cache purge.
